
SMTP = *Simple Mail Transfer Protocol*

sa:

  The → Windows/PowerShell/language/variable/preference[PowerShell preference variable] `$PSEmailServer` specifies the default SMTP server for the PowerShell cmdlet
 `→ Windows/PowerShell/command-inventory/noun/mailMessage/send`.

 `dnsdiag.exe` (`→ Windows/dirs/Program-Files-x86/Windows-Resource-Kits/Tools`) is an *SMTP DNS Diagnostic Program*.

  The Oracle package `→ development/databases/Oracle/installed/packages/utl/smtp`

  The Perl modules → development/languages/Perl/modules/Net/SMTP[`Net::SMTP`], `Email::Sender::Transport::SMTP` etc.
